                        <interp inst="t18360509-name-1451" type="given" value="JOHN BOND"></interp>JOHN BOND RATCLIFFE</persName>
                  </hi>. I was going through Union-street, South-wark, on the 20th of April, about half-past four o'clock, and stopped to allow some carriages to pass—I felt my handkerchief drawn from me—I turned and saw the prisoner crossing the road with it under his arm—I took it from him and gave him into custody.</p>
